description:
Nothing is better than following a God-inspired path. 
“Show Me Your Ways” by the Sapphire Singers was originally aired at the General Conference Session 2022. The group is from Australia and is part of the South Pacific Division of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.

Lyrics: 
Here I am, Oh Lord, I lift up my eyes to You 
Lord, having strayed so far from You, from where I stand before 
Lord, I know that I have to turn back from my sins and follow You 

Show me Your ways that I may walk with You 
And give me the courage to stand like the brave
Cause You're my guiding Light when I'm alone in the dark
My very Helper in times of need
It’s You and You alone I deserve. 

Lord, I know there is no safer place than this
You're always there to hold me 
And in my darkest days when I've lost my sight
Lord, I know that I have to turn back from my sins and follow You 

Show me Your ways that I may walk with You 
And give me the courage to stand like the brave
Cause You're my guiding Light when I'm alone in the dark
My very Helper in times of need
It’s You and You alone I deserve
